Code.NativeIaC:
```bicep
// Bicep: Switch a Cosmos DB account to Continuous backup (irreversible)
resource account 'Microsoft.DocumentDB/databaseAccounts@2025-10-15' = {
  name: '<example_resource_name>'
  location: resourceGroup().location
  kind: 'GlobalDocumentDB'
  properties: {
    databaseAccountOfferType: 'Standard'
    locations: [{ locationName: resourceGroup().location }]
    backupPolicy: {
      type: 'Continuous' // Critical: Enables point-in-time restore. Migration from Periodic is one-way.
      continuousModeProperties: {
        tier: 'Continuous30Days' // or 'Continuous7Days' for the lower-cost tier
      }
    }
  }
}
```

Code.Terraform:
```hcl
# Terraform: Configure Cosmos DB account with Continuous backup (irreversible)
resource "azurerm_cosmosdb_account" "<example_resource_name>" {
  name                = "<example_resource_name>"
  resource_group_name = "<example_resource_name>"
  location            = "<example_resource_name>"
  offer_type          = "Standard"
  kind                = "GlobalDocumentDB"

  geo_location {
    location          = "<example_resource_name>"
    failover_priority = 0
  }

  backup {
    type = "Continuous"          # Critical: Enables point-in-time restore. One-way migration from Periodic.
    tier = "Continuous30Days"    # or "Continuous7Days" for the lower-cost tier
  }
}
```
